    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I gave #p406# 1000 mesos as commission for telling me about various requests from the citizens of #m10003000#. The first request is from #p409#, the owner of the armor shop, who needs materials to craft new armor. I need to defeat #b20 #o9#s#k and #b20 #o10#s#k and collect #b10 #t4000009#s#k and #b10 #t4000010#s#k. It shouldn't be too hard, since #o9#s and #o10#s are commonly found near #m10003000#."
    },
    "2": {
      "_dirName": "2",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I delivered what #p409# asked for and got bunch of #t2010005#s in return. I wonder what kind of armor #p409# will make. Nella said there are many more requests I can do. I should visit #p406# every once in a while."
