  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Whoa, I haven't seen you before! I'm guessing you're not from here. My name's #b#p406##k, and I know everything that goes on around town. That's right, I'm always the first with any juicy pieces of news!"
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "For #b1000 mesos#k, I can gather some intel and hook you up with work. You game? Think of me as your agent! I get a cut, but you get a gig."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Awesome! Like I promised, you give me 1000 mesos, I give you the hook-ups. I'm so efficient, I have your first job right here. #b#p409##k from the armor store has been collecting rare items for a new piece of armor he's trying to create."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "It shouldn't be too hard for you to defeat #b20 #o9#s#k and #b20 #o10#s#k, and get me #b10 #t4000009#s#k and #b10 #t4000010#s#k, right? Once you get me the goods, I'll slide you your reward. Now get to work!"
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Hey, it's your call. You change your mind, you give me a call."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Got the goods? Excellent! Here's your reward. #b#p409##k has provided a bunch of #b#t2010005#s#k as payment. Use them well!"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Alright, if you need work sometime down the road, feel free to come back and see me."
        }
      },
